  <entry>
    <title>你好，世界！</title>
    <url>/2021/05/25/First-Test/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="你好，世界！"><a href="#你好，世界！" class="headerlink" title="你好，世界！"></a>你好，世界！</h2><span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="轻轻迎来第一束阳光"><a href="#轻轻迎来第一束阳光" class="headerlink" title="轻轻迎来第一束阳光"></a>轻轻迎来第一束阳光</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//C</span><br><span class="line">include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">int <span class="function"><span class="title">main</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello, world!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">return</span> 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="生命中第一杯茶"><a href="#生命中第一杯茶" class="headerlink" title="生命中第一杯茶"></a>生命中第一杯茶</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//C++</span><br><span class="line">include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line">int <span class="function"><span class="title">main</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Hello, world!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">endl;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="生命中第一声欢笑"><a href="#生命中第一声欢笑" class="headerlink" title="生命中第一声欢笑"></a>生命中第一声欢笑</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Python</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Hello, world!&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="生命中第一次流泪"><a href="#生命中第一次流泪" class="headerlink" title="生命中第一次流泪"></a>生命中第一次流泪</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/*JavaScript*/</span><br><span class="line">alert(<span class="string">&#x27;Hello, world!&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="生命中…"><a href="#生命中…" class="headerlink" title="生命中…"></a>生命中…</h3><h2 id="我一直在这里，我一直在这里等你"><a href="#我一直在这里，我一直在这里等你" class="headerlink" title="我一直在这里，我一直在这里等你"></a>我一直在这里，我一直在这里等你</h2>]]></content>
